-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- 0009_price_corrections.sql
-- Purpose: correct master SKU prices for Bedframes (BF) and Sofas (SF) from
--   the authoritative Production Sheet (v5, 2026-04-23).
-- Scope: updates products.basePriceSen / products.price1Sen /
--   products.seatHeightPrices and product_dept_configs.price2Sen.
-- Safe to re-apply (UPDATEs are idempotent).
-- Rows that don't exist in the DB are silently skipped (no-op).
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

